title: Police: Woman missing, endangered in Pierce County area
text:
A woman, Ceslie Anne Acuna, has gone missing out of the Pierce County area.
She was last heard from while returning a vehicle to her ex-boyfriend, Joel Brent Boots, Sr.
She has mental issues and could be in danger, according to family.
#MasonCo .: Missing Ceslie Acuna has mental issues, may be in danger. Person of interest: ex-boyfriend Joel Boots. pic.twitter.com/SA9cM6JVq7
â€” KIRO 7 (@KIRO7Seattle) October 10, 2015 Ceslie is described by police as a 36-year-old white woman with brown hair (dyed blonde) and brown eyes.
If you see either Ceslie or Joel, you are asked to contact detectives at: JRhoades@co.mason.wa.us or 360-427-9670, ext. 627, case # 15-14536.
